---
import Console from "../components/Console.astro";
---

<section
  id="hero"
  class="relative h-dvh min-h-[600px] flex items-center overflow-hidden mx-auto px-6 md:px-10"
>
  {/* Background Image Layer */}
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 z-0 bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat opacity-60"
    style={{
      backgroundImage: "url('/hero-background.webp')",
    }}
  >
  </div>

  {/* Dark Gradient Overlay for readability */}
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 z-0 bg-linear-to-r from-[#050a14] via-[#050a14]/80 to-[#050a14]/30"
  >
  </div>
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 z-0 bg-linear-to-t from-[#050a14] via-transparent to-transparent"
  >
  </div>

  {/* Content */}
  <div
    class="container relative flex flex-col h-full justify-center z-10 mx-auto mt-0 md:mt-10"
  >
    <h1
      class="font-bold text-tertiary tracking-tight leading-[1.05] text-[clamp(2.25rem,6vw,4.5rem)]"
    >
      Andrés Camilo
    </h1>
    <h2
      class="font-light text-secondary leading-snug mb-4 text-[clamp(1.5rem,3.6vw,3rem)]"
    >
      Full-Stack Developer
    </h2>
    <p
      class="text-primary leading-relaxed mt-2 mb-8 text-[clamp(1rem,1.2vw,1.25rem)] w-full sm:w-4/5 lg:w-1/2 max-w-[65ch]"
    >
      Desarrollador web especializado en aplicaciones web y móviles, enfocado en
      diseñar experiencias de usuario intuitivas, rendimiento eficiente y
      soluciones escalables. Combino diseño centrado en el usuario y buenas
      prácticas de ingeniería para convertir ideas en productos digitales
      atractivos y robustos.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center gap-4">
      <a
        href="#projects"
        class="btn-line w-full sm:w-auto text-center hover:bg-accent hover:text-primary px-6 py-3 text-base sm:text-lg"
        >ver mis proyectos</a
      >
    </div>

    {/* Code Overlay Layer (Decorative) */}
    <Console />
  </div>
</section>
